 Salihu Tanko Salihu Tanko Yakasai, former media aide to Abdullahi Ganduje, governor of Kano, has travelled out of the country. In a Twitter post on Wednesday, Yakasai, popularly known as Dawisu, said “goodbye” to Nigeria. He did not indicate where he was heading to, but he shared pictures of himself at the airport and the airline he was flying with. “Japa….. Goodbye Naija! Alhamdulilah!” he wrote. Japa….. Goodbye Naija! Alhamdulilah! ? pic.twitter.com/MHz4lVFt2M — Peacock (@dawisu) March 17, 2021